&lt;li&gt;Have several years of experience in technical program management, with a track record of successfully delivering complex, cross-functional programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess deep technical knowledge that allows you to engage meaningfully with ML researchers and engineers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have experience managing programs with significant external dependencies and multiple stakeholder groups&lt;/li&gt;
